Also including a `z` value in your points is also valid and does not require having the `getX` & `getY` callbacks.

```javascript
// z coordinate (does not require Get callbacks)
const pointsZ = [[110, 60, 4000], [130, 40, 3000]];
kdbush(pointsZ);
```

